<br>
1) Ask the people it affected to e-mail Verant with a detailed description of what happened.  Hopefully they'll be able to be reimbursed, but if not, at least it will give Verant the details to help track down the exploit &amp; fix it.<br>
<br>
2) I'd recommend that no one put valuable items in trade.  If someone wants to see the stats, send them a /tell with the link in it.  If they say they don't have the new UI, just tell them the stats.<br>
<br>
3) If you're making a trade with valuable items with someone you don't know well (let's say someone wants to buy your eyepatch of plunder), agree on a well known 3rd party to handle the trade for you (ie: one person gives her the cash, the other the eyepatch, and then she hands back the items/cash to the new owners).<br>
<br>
A little bit of a hassle, but less so than having someone run off with your equipment.<br>
